00:09:46.330 --> 00:09:47.677 align:middle line:90%
What am I doing here?

00:09:47.677 --> 00:09:48.760 align:middle line:90%
What's my purpose in life?

00:09:48.760 --> 00:09:49.802 align:middle line:90%
What happens when we die?

00:09:49.802 --> 00:09:51.290 align:middle line:90%
Is it really about success?

00:09:51.290 --> 00:09:52.840 align:middle line:90%
What is it about?

00:09:52.840 --> 00:09:55.810 align:middle line:84%
And that started
my inward journey.

00:09:55.810 --> 00:09:57.940 align:middle line:84%
And asking those
big questions, I

00:09:57.940 --> 00:10:02.470 align:middle line:84%
think that you have to open
up doors of possibility

00:10:02.470 --> 00:10:07.480 align:middle line:84%
and look to see for answers
