00:30:45.410 --> 00:30:49.760 align:middle line:84%
They begin to expect the
same outcome as the past.

00:30:49.760 --> 00:30:52.460 align:middle line:84%
And the anticipation
of the event

00:30:52.460 --> 00:30:54.770 align:middle line:84%
causes the body
to naturally begin

00:30:54.770 --> 00:30:56.660 align:middle line:90%
to make its own chemicals.

00:30:56.660 --> 00:31:01.700 align:middle line:84%
So that pill then is a
symbol of possibility.

00:31:01.700 --> 00:31:04.670 align:middle line:84%
And the moment that
person gets that pill,

00:31:04.670 --> 00:31:07.280 align:middle line:84%
they begin to select the
potential in the quantum field

00:31:07.280 --> 00:31:09.040 align:middle line:90%
called getting better.

00:31:09.040 --> 00:31:10.760 align:middle line:84%
And a certain percentage
of those people

00:31:10.760 --> 00:31:15.620 align:middle line:84%
begin to become optimistic,
excited, inspired, grateful.

00:31:15.620 --> 00:31:17.300 align:middle line:84%
And when you combine
a clear intention

00:31:17.300 --> 00:31:19.250 align:middle line:84%
with an elevated
emotion, you just

00:31:19.250 --> 00:31:22.280 align:middle line:84%
changed your biology from living
in the past, present reality

00:31:22.280 --> 00:31:25.620 align:middle line:84%
to living in a future
present reality.

00:31:25.620 --> 00:31:28.790 align:middle line:84%
And when a person moves into
that future present reality,

00:31:28.790 --> 00:31:30.950 align:middle line:90%
they're in a new state of being.

00:31:30.950 --> 00:31:33.530 align:middle line:84%
And that will begin to program
their autonomic nervous system

00:31:33.530 --> 00:31:36.560 align:middle line:84%
to make the pharmaceuticals
equal to the substance they

00:31:36.560 --> 00:31:38.010 align:middle line:90%
think they're taking.

00:31:38.010 --> 00:31:41.265 align:middle line:84%
So the fundamental question
is, do you need a sugar pill?

00:31:41.265 --> 00:31:43.580 align:middle line:84%
Do you need a saline
injection to do that?

00:31:43.580 --> 00:31:45.620 align:middle line:84%
Or can you combine
a clear intention

00:31:45.620 --> 00:31:49.200 align:middle line:84%
with an elevated emotion and
move into a new state of being?

00:31:49.200 --> 00:31:52.340 align:middle line:84%
In other words, instead
of selecting a known,

00:31:52.340 --> 00:31:56.210 align:middle line:84%
selecting an unknown and
keep revisiting that unknown

00:31:56.210 --> 00:31:59.960 align:middle line:84%
until it becomes a known and
your biology begins to change?

00:31:59.960 --> 00:32:02.300 align:middle line:84%
And the answer is
absolutely yes.

00:32:02.300 --> 00:32:07.070 align:middle line:84%
So my interest was,
OK, so if I understood

00:32:07.070 --> 00:32:10.160 align:middle line:84%
the mechanics of
the placebo and how

00:32:10.160 --> 00:32:12.800 align:middle line:84%
it works from a
scientific standpoint,

00:32:12.800 --> 00:32:15.300 align:middle line:90%
can you teach people to do it?

00:32:15.300 --> 00:32:17.330 align:middle line:84%
And the answer is
absolutely yes.

00:32:17.330 --> 00:32:19.610 align:middle line:90%
Now, there's some conditions.

00:32:19.610 --> 00:32:21.440 align:middle line:84%
For example, in
depression studies,

00:32:21.440 --> 00:32:25.220 align:middle line:84%
81% of people that are
in depression study

00:32:25.220 --> 00:32:29.090 align:middle line:84%
get better in taking a placebo
or the substance the placebo

00:32:29.090 --> 00:32:32.300 align:middle line:84%
works as well as the
antidepressant that the control

00:32:32.300 --> 00:32:34.260 align:middle line:90%
group is taking.

00:32:34.260 --> 00:32:39.260 align:middle line:84%
So 81% of those
people are making

00:32:39.260 --> 00:32:42.120 align:middle line:84%
their own anti-depressants
