00:50:50.830 --> 00:50:52.330 align:middle line:84%
So now she's
emotionally imbalanced.

00:50:52.330 --> 00:50:53.830 align:middle line:84%
And now she's
chemically imbalanced.

00:50:53.830 --> 00:50:56.890 align:middle line:84%
And she's physically imbalanced
because she's injured.

00:50:56.890 --> 00:50:58.510 align:middle line:84%
So a few months
after that, she's

00:50:58.510 --> 00:51:00.970 align:middle line:90%
having problems swallowing.

00:51:00.970 --> 00:51:04.480 align:middle line:84%
And they find a tumor
right above her stomach.

00:51:04.480 --> 00:51:07.360 align:middle line:90%
And she has esophageal cancer.

00:51:07.360 --> 00:51:11.020 align:middle line:84%
And the doctor told her that
she had a very short amount

00:51:11.020 --> 00:51:12.460 align:middle line:90%
of time to live.

00:51:12.460 --> 00:51:17.940 align:middle line:84%
Now, she came to a workshop
that we were doing in Holland.

00:51:17.940 --> 00:51:19.620 align:middle line:84%
And I remember the
day she came in

00:51:19.620 --> 00:51:21.130 align:middle line:84%
because she came
in with crutches

00:51:21.130 --> 00:51:24.740 align:middle line:84%
and she sat in a room of
about 500 people on the side.

00:51:24.740 --> 00:51:27.120 align:middle line:84%
And I saw her walker
and her crutches.

00:51:27.120 --> 00:51:29.760 align:middle line:84%
Now, she is a psychologist,
psychotherapist.

00:51:29.760 --> 00:51:31.880 align:middle line:90%
She is an educated woman.

00:51:31.880 --> 00:51:33.010 align:middle line:90%
Got a master's.

00:51:33.010 --> 00:51:34.960 align:middle line:90%
She treats conditions.

00:51:34.960 --> 00:51:38.513 align:middle line:84%
She could, from a
psychological standpoint,

00:51:38.513 --> 00:51:40.180 align:middle line:84%
have the insight of
how it all happened,

00:51:40.180 --> 00:51:41.980 align:middle line:90%
but she couldn't change it.

00:51:41.980 --> 00:51:45.340 align:middle line:84%
She did one chemotherapy
treatment for the cancer.

00:51:45.340 --> 00:51:47.260 align:middle line:84%
And she said it just
about killed her.

00:51:47.260 --> 00:51:49.630 align:middle line:90%
And she stopped.

00:51:49.630 --> 00:51:52.600 align:middle line:90%
So she came to our event.

00:51:52.600 --> 00:51:54.430 align:middle line:90%
And she started doing the work.

00:51:54.430 --> 00:51:57.550 align:middle line:90%
And she had a lot of doubt.

00:51:57.550 --> 00:51:59.530 align:middle line:90%
And she had a lot of fear.

00:51:59.530 --> 00:52:02.150 align:middle line:84%
She didn't feel like doing
her meditation certain days.

00:52:02.150 --> 00:52:06.550 align:middle line:84%
But every single day by creating
the elevated emotion combined

00:52:06.550 --> 00:52:09.610 align:middle line:84%
with a clear intention and
changing her state of being

00:52:09.610 --> 00:52:14.330 align:middle line:84%
and overcoming the
past every single day

00:52:14.330 --> 00:52:19.900 align:middle line:84%
in a matter of about a year,
all of her cancer disappeared.

00:52:19.900 --> 00:52:21.400 align:middle line:90%
The tumor shrunk.

00:52:21.400 --> 00:52:25.060 align:middle line:84%
All the ulcerations on all her
mucous membranes went away.

00:52:25.060 --> 00:52:27.300 align:middle line:90%
She has no paralysis, no pain.

00:52:27.300 --> 00:52:28.870 align:middle line:90%
She has no depression.

00:52:28.870 --> 00:52:34.040 align:middle line:84%
She owns a hospital
now in Holland.

00:52:34.040 --> 00:52:37.780 align:middle line:84%
She's one of my executive
corporate trainers.

00:52:37.780 --> 00:52:40.330 align:middle line:84%
And she has a new
husband and a great guy.

00:52:40.330 --> 00:52:42.520 align:middle line:90%
And he's a successful person.

00:52:42.520 --> 00:52:45.160 align:middle line:90%
And she's in love with life.

00:52:45.160 --> 00:52:50.000 align:middle line:84%
And so we have people that
heal from cancer quite a bit.

00:52:50.000 --> 00:52:52.900 align:middle line:84%
And I'm going to tell you, it
takes an uncompromising world

00:52:52.900 --> 00:52:53.920 align:middle line:90%
to do it.

00:52:53.920 --> 00:52:58.390 align:middle line:84%
But the beauty behind it is
when she stands on the stage

00:52:58.390 --> 00:53:02.800 align:middle line:84%
and she tells her story and
she doesn't look any different

00:53:02.800 --> 00:53:04.180 align:middle line:90%
than anybody else--

00:53:04.180 --> 00:53:05.950 align:middle line:90%
she's not wearing white.

00:53:05.950 --> 00:53:08.110 align:middle line:90%
She's not young and fit.

00:53:08.110 --> 00:53:09.930 align:middle line:90%
She's just a common person--

00:53:09.930 --> 00:53:13.330 align:middle line:84%
that so many people,
when they hear the story

00:53:13.330 --> 00:53:16.330 align:middle line:84%
begin to change their belief
about what's possible.

00:53:16.330 --> 00:53:19.180 align:middle line:84%
And because of her
and a few other people

00:53:19.180 --> 00:53:21.160 align:middle line:84%
that heal themselves
of ovarian cancer

00:53:21.160 --> 00:53:24.430 align:middle line:84%
and a few other big cancers,
when they tell their story,

00:53:24.430 --> 00:53:27.440 align:middle line:84%
more and more people are
accepting that it's possible.

00:53:27.440 --> 00:53:29.080 align:middle line:84%
And that's how we
change the paradigm.

00:53:29.080 --> 00:53:32.500 align:middle line:84%
It's no longer the philosophical
component that does it.

00:53:32.500 --> 00:53:34.120 align:middle line:84%
It's the example
of it that does it.

00:53:34.120 --> 00:53:37.510 align:middle line:84%
And to me, she is the
living example of truth.

00:53:37.510 --> 00:53:40.480 align:middle line:84%
So then so the interesting
thing about that

00:53:40.480 --> 00:53:42.730 align:middle line:84%
is that if you ask
her about her past,

00:53:42.730 --> 00:53:45.520 align:middle line:84%
she will tell you that it
was the best thing that

00:53:45.520 --> 00:53:47.170 align:middle line:90%
ever happened to her.

00:53:47.170 --> 00:53:49.180 align:middle line:84%
And if you ask her
about her disease,

00:53:49.180 --> 00:53:54.280 align:middle line:84%
she will tell you the disease
lives in the old personality.

00:53:54.280 --> 00:53:56.260 align:middle line:90%
I'm literally somebody else.

00:53:56.260 --> 00:53:59.650 align:middle line:84%
And just like a person with
multiple personality disorder

00:53:59.650 --> 00:54:02.650 align:middle line:84%
that has an allergy to nylon
stockings in one personality

00:54:02.650 --> 00:54:05.480 align:middle line:84%
and type 2 diabetes in
another personality,

00:54:05.480 --> 00:54:07.630 align:middle line:84%
she literally
became someone else.

00:54:07.630 --> 00:54:10.180 align:middle line:84%
And the disease exists
in the old person.

00:54:10.180 --> 00:54:14.110 align:middle line:84%
Now, the beauty behind
her is that she understood

00:54:14.110 --> 00:54:17.140 align:middle line:84%
that the emotion, if she could
truly be present and hold

00:54:17.140 --> 00:54:20.440 align:middle line:84%
an image and rehearse
a future and begin

00:54:20.440 --> 00:54:22.240 align:middle line:84%
to create the emotion,
her brain and body

00:54:22.240 --> 00:54:25.820 align:middle line:84%
would change from living in the
past to living in the future.

00:54:25.820 --> 00:54:28.000 align:middle line:84%
So then if she's feeling
fear every single day,

00:54:28.000 --> 00:54:30.580 align:middle line:84%
then she's in the past,
because the moment

00:54:30.580 --> 00:54:32.900 align:middle line:84%
she wakes up and
searches for that feeling

00:54:32.900 --> 00:54:35.290 align:middle line:84%
and she gets in touch with
that feeling, that feeling is

00:54:35.290 --> 00:54:37.720 align:middle line:84%
a record of the past and starts
influencing her thoughts,

00:54:37.720 --> 00:54:40.420 align:middle line:84%
then her entire state
of being is in the past.

00:54:40.420 --> 00:54:42.700 align:middle line:84%
Every day as she
starts overcoming

00:54:42.700 --> 00:54:44.800 align:middle line:84%
those emotions and those
doubts and those thoughts

00:54:44.800 --> 00:54:47.920 align:middle line:84%
and attitudes and
hardwired behaviors,

00:54:47.920 --> 00:54:49.472 align:middle line:84%
she's changing her
neurocircuitry.

00:54:49.472 --> 00:54:50.680 align:middle line:90%
She's changing her chemistry.

00:54:50.680 --> 00:54:52.060 align:middle line:90%
She's changing her hormones.

00:54:52.060 --> 00:54:53.590 align:middle line:90%
She's even changing her genes.

00:54:53.590 --> 00:54:56.590 align:middle line:84%
And because she studied
it and she understood it,

00:54:56.590 --> 00:54:58.510 align:middle line:84%
she understood what
she was doing and why,

00:54:58.510 --> 00:55:00.130 align:middle line:90%
and the how it got easier.

00:55:00.130 --> 00:55:03.790 align:middle line:84%
And she said, which I
thought was so beautiful,

00:55:03.790 --> 00:55:07.360 align:middle line:84%
I'm not getting up
from this meditation

00:55:07.360 --> 00:55:09.460 align:middle line:90%
until I'm in love with life.

00:55:09.460 --> 00:55:13.930 align:middle line:84%
Now to the materialist
who's looking for evidence,

00:55:13.930 --> 00:55:16.240 align:middle line:84%
