be in love with life.

00:55:16.240 --> 00:55:17.570 align:middle line:90%
She lost her husband.

00:55:17.570 --> 00:55:19.010 align:middle line:90%
She was in financial crisis.

00:55:19.010 --> 00:55:19.970 align:middle line:90%
She lost her job.

00:55:19.970 --> 00:55:20.932 align:middle line:90%
She had no friends.

00:55:20.932 --> 00:55:22.390 align:middle line:84%
She couldn't take
care of her kids.

00:55:22.390 --> 00:55:23.240 align:middle line:90%
She was paralyzed.

00:55:23.240 --> 00:55:24.040 align:middle line:90%
She had cancer.

00:55:24.040 --> 00:55:24.840 align:middle line:90%
She had depression.

00:55:24.840 --> 00:55:26.340 align:middle line:90%
She had ulcerations.

