But she said, I'm going to
teach my body emotionally

00:55:31.200 --> 00:55:34.780 align:middle line:84%
what my future is going to feel
like before it's made manifest.

00:55:34.780 --> 00:55:37.860 align:middle line:84%
And over time, overcoming,
overcoming, overcoming,

00:55:37.860 --> 00:55:39.460 align:middle line:90%
she became someone else.

00:55:39.460 --> 00:55:43.770 align:middle line:84%
And I just had dinner with
her in Switzerland last month.

00:55:43.770 --> 00:55:46.807 align:middle line:84%
And she said, you know, I'm
so in love with my life.

