want to demonstrate?

01:00:23.700 --> 01:00:26.380 align:middle line:84%
If you keep firing and wiring
those circuits over and over

01:00:26.380 --> 01:00:28.770 align:middle line:84%
again, it's going to begin
become familiar to you.

01:00:28.770 --> 01:00:31.540 align:middle line:84%
