elevated emotional states,

01:00:31.540 --> 01:00:33.340 align:middle line:84%
just like you cultivate
fear or guilt,

01:00:33.340 --> 01:00:35.080 align:middle line:84%
if you keep doing
that enough times,

01:00:35.080 --> 01:00:37.390 align:middle line:84%
it's going to begin to
become familiar to you.

01:00:37.390 --> 01:00:40.880 align:middle line:84%
