change and transition.

01:00:40.880 --> 01:00:43.240 align:middle line:84%
And so we use the
model of meditation

01:00:43.240 --> 01:00:45.880 align:middle line:84%
because the whole
purpose of meditation

01:00:45.880 --> 01:00:48.290 align:middle line:84%
is to get beyond
the analytical mind.

01:00:48.290 --> 01:00:51.700 align:middle line:84%
And what separates the conscious
mind from the subconscious mind

01:00:51.700 --> 01:00:53.510 align:middle line:90%
is the analytical mind.

01:00:53.510 --> 01:00:56.830 align:middle line:84%
So then we have ways in
different meditations

01:00:56.830 --> 01:01:00.420 align:middle line:84%
to teach our students how
to change their brainwaves,

01:01:00.420 --> 01:01:02.630 align:middle line:84%
from that high
alert beta brainwave

01:01:02.630 --> 01:01:05.880 align:middle line:84%
state that switches on when
a person's in chronic stress

01:01:05.880 --> 01:01:07.500 align:middle line:84%
to be able to
regulate and change

01:01:07.500 --> 01:01:10.140 align:middle line:84%
their brainwaves, to teach
them how to go from focusing

01:01:10.140 --> 01:01:13.110 align:middle line:84%
on matter and objects and
things to focusing on nothing,

01:01:13.110 --> 01:01:15.480 align:middle line:84%
to focusing on space, to
go from a narrow focus

01:01:15.480 --> 01:01:16.500 align:middle line:90%
to an open focus.

01:01:16.500 --> 01:01:19.930 align:middle line:84%
And when that occurs,
brainwaves begin to slow down.

01:01:19.930 --> 01:01:21.900 align:middle line:84%
And if they're sensing
space and they're not

01:01:21.900 --> 01:01:24.510 align:middle line:84%
analyzing and thinking,
different compartments

01:01:24.510 --> 01:01:26.520 align:middle line:84%
of the brain that
were once subdivided

01:01:26.520 --> 01:01:28.650 align:middle line:84%
because the hormones of
stress because they're

01:01:28.650 --> 01:01:30.960 align:middle line:84%
shifting their attention to
their kids, to their wife,

01:01:30.960 --> 01:01:33.168 align:middle line:84%
to their job, to their
problems, to their cell phone,

01:01:33.168 --> 01:01:35.070 align:middle line:84%
