one of those things

01:01:35.070 --> 01:01:36.870 align:middle line:84%
is a neurological
network in our brain.

01:01:36.870 --> 01:01:39.900 align:middle line:84%
Keep doing that, the brain
starts firing incoherently.

01:01:39.900 --> 01:01:42.030 align:middle line:84%
When the brain's incoherent,
we're incoherent.

01:01:42.030 --> 01:01:44.580 align:middle line:84%
When the brain isn't working
right, we're not working right.

01:01:44.580 --> 01:01:48.000 align:middle line:84%
So by regulating and changing
brainwaves and teaching

01:01:48.000 --> 01:01:51.480 align:middle line:84%
our students how to
do it, in time then

01:01:51.480 --> 01:01:53.588 align:middle line:90%
the brain starts to synchronize.

01:01:53.588 --> 01:01:55.380 align:middle line:84%
If you're no longer
analyzing and thinking,

01:01:55.380 --> 01:01:57.480 align:middle line:84%
the autonomic nervous
system steps in,

01:01:57.480 --> 01:02:00.390 align:middle line:84%
which is its job is to
create order and balance,

01:02:00.390 --> 01:02:02.250 align:middle line:84%
as your brainwaves
change, you begin

01:02:02.250 --> 01:02:06.300 align:middle line:84%
to make contact and go from beta
brainwaves to alpha brainwaves.

01:02:06.300 --> 01:02:09.210 align:middle line:84%
And when that occurs, all of a
sudden different compartments

01:02:09.210 --> 01:02:10.830 align:middle line:84%
of the brain that
were once subdivided

01:02:10.830 --> 01:02:12.140 align:middle line:90%
start to synchronize.

01:02:12.140 --> 01:02:14.520 align:middle line:84%
And what syncs in the
brain, links in the brain.

01:02:14.520 --> 01:02:16.488 align:middle line:84%
And all of sudden, we
start feeling more whole.

01:02:16.488 --> 01:02:18.030 align:middle line:84%
And it's the autonomic
nervous system

01:02:18.030 --> 01:02:21.120 align:middle line:84%
then that starts to regulate
balance and in the neocortex,

01:02:21.120 --> 01:02:24.300 align:middle line:84%
and we start feeling
more in balance.

01:02:24.300 --> 01:02:27.660 align:middle line:84%
So to regulate and change
the brainwaves, when

01:02:27.660 --> 01:02:29.250 align:middle line:84%
you go from beta
to alpha, you're

01:02:29.250 --> 01:02:31.530 align:middle line:84%
moving right beyond
the analytical mind.

01:02:31.530 --> 01:02:33.600 align:middle line:84%
